{
  "stem": "25348.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was just about going to make good his word that he will punch me in the nose.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lucky for me, a very attractive woman came in and she didn't ask him, but he followed her with the eyes and he was more interested in her than he was in me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She parked her pram-- I didn't realize that this was fairly common practice there-- her baby pram downstairs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she walked up the stairs to an officer's room and he followed her and this is how I-- and saved me from getting a beating.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was at that time that I sort of had a different perspective on the parade of baby prams.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "These women, they didn't know whether they widows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a bit of promiscuity-- I don't think there were real tarts, but there was much promiscuity going on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they disappeared into the officers' rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Anyhow, I worked at the-- this hotel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Suddenly, one day, there were different noises.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I looked out the little window, and there were Germans changing in the street into civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The war was over, but nobody said so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I get up, and I see every door of every room open, and I ask someone brushing past me, where is Herr Pabst?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, how should I know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the end of the Third Reich-- not officially yet-- and it was an end to a thousand-year dream.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was-- was about the 6th of May, 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm telling you about two days before the capitulation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was fighting with my thoughts, one minute hoping, one minute despairing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
